{
  "_resourceType": "script",
  "id": "f0a1b2c3-d4e5-4f60-8a1b-2c3d4e5f6071",
  "name": "Read Area Sign",
  "description": "Shows a signboard message for the Sign the player faces. Switches on CurrentArea (var 22, set by each scene's On Init), then on the sign's X tile (PlayerX var12); where several signs share an X, a nested switch on the Y tile (PlayerY var13) picks the right one. Unmatched signs fall through to the area sign. Called from the overworld A-button handler when the player faces a Sign metatile (id 125).",
